SELECT
  DATEADD(HOUR, -7, em500.timestamp) as Time,
  em500.temp as Temperature
FROM
  em500_pt100_data em500
  LEFT JOIN site_detail sd ON em500.site_id = sd.id
WHERE
  timestamp >= DATEADD(HOUR, 7, $__timeFrom())
  AND timestamp <= DATEADD(HOUR, 7, $__timeTo())
  AND sd.site_name = 'T-SAT Tank-01'
ORDER BY
  timestamp ASC

SELECT
  TOP(100)
  batch_no AS "Batch no.",
  date_start AS "Start date",
  start_time AS "Start time",
  date_stop AS "Stop date",
  stop_time AS "Stop time"
FROM sap
ORDER BY date_start DESC, start_time DESC --  Batch

SELECT TOP 1
    CASE
        WHEN MAX(DATEADD(HOUR, -7, em500.[timestamp])) IS NULL THEN 0 
        WHEN MAX(DATEADD(HOUR, -7, em500.[timestamp])) >= DATEADD(MINUTE, -30, GETDATE()) THEN 1 
        ELSE 0
    END AS 'T-SAT Tank-01'
FROM
    em500_pt100_data em500
JOIN
    site_detail sd ON em500.site_id = sd.id
WHERE
    sd.site_name = 'T-SAT Tank-01'

SELECT TOP 1
    CASE
        WHEN MAX(DATEADD(HOUR, -7, em320.[timestamp])) IS NULL THEN 0 
        WHEN MAX(DATEADD(HOUR, -7, em320.[timestamp])) >= DATEADD(MINUTE, -30, GETDATE()) THEN 1 
        ELSE 0
    END AS 'TH-Outside'
FROM
    em320_th_data em320
JOIN
    site_detail sd ON em320.site_id = sd.id
WHERE
    sd.site_name = 'TH-Outside'

SELECT TOP 1
    CASE
        WHEN MAX(DATEADD(HOUR, -7, o3.[timestamp])) IS NULL THEN 0 
        WHEN MAX(DATEADD(HOUR, -7, o3.[timestamp])) >= DATEADD(MINUTE, -30, GETDATE()) THEN 1 
        ELSE 0
    END AS 'O3-Outside'
FROM
    o3_data o3
JOIN
    site_detail sd ON o3.site_id = sd.id
WHERE
    sd.site_name = 'O3-Outside'

--- SELECT sp.batch_no,em320.temp_min,em320.temp_max,em320.temp_avg,em320.temp_min,em320.temp_max,em320.temp_avg,o3.oz_min,o3.oz_max,o3.oz_avg
SELECT sp.batch_no AS [Batch no.] ,
        CASE -- temp min
            WHEN em320.temp_min <= em500.temp_min THEN em320.temp_min
            ELSE em500.temp_min
        END AS [Min Temperature],
        CASE -- temp max
            WHEN em320.temp_max >= em500.temp_max THEN em320.temp_max
            ELSE em500.temp_max
        END AS [Max Temperature], 
        (em320.temp_avg + em500.temp_avg)/ 2 as [Average Temperature],
        em320.humid_min as [Min Humidity],
        em320.humid_max as [Max Humidity],
        em320.humid_avg as [Average Humidity],
        o3.oz_min [Min Ozone],
        o3.oz_max [Max Ozone],
        o3.oz_avg [Average Ozone]
        
FROM sap sp
LEFT JOIN em320_th_sap em320
ON sp.batch_no = em320.batch_no
LEFT JOIN em500_pt100_sap em500
ON sp.batch_no = em500.batch_no
LEFT JOIN o3_sap o3
ON sp.batch_no = o3.batch_no

WHERE sp.start_time >= DATEADD(HOUR, 7, $__timeFrom())
  AND sp.start_time <= DATEADD(HOUR, 7, $__timeTo())
ORDER BY sp.start_time DESC

SELECT 
    s.batch_no,
    AVG(o.oz_avg) AS [Avg Ozone (All)],

    -- 2. Tank Temp ()
    AVG(t.temp_avg) AS [Avg Tank Temp (All)],

    -- 3. Room Temp/Humid ()
    AVG(th.temp_avg) AS [Avg Room Temp (All)],
    AVG(th.humid_avg) AS [Avg Room Humid (All)]

FROM sap s
-- Join  LEFT JOIN ( Batch  Sensor  error)
LEFT JOIN o3_sap o ON s.batch_no = o.batch_no
LEFT JOIN em500_pt100_sap t ON s.batch_no = t.batch_no
LEFT JOIN em320_th_sap th ON s.batch_no = th.batch_no

--  Group By  1 Batch  Sensor 
GROUP BY s.batch_no

SELECT 
    s.batch_no as [Batch no.],

    (
        SELECT MIN(temp_val) --  2 
        FROM (
            SELECT temp_min AS temp_val FROM em320_th_sap WHERE batch_no = s.batch_no
            UNION ALL
            SELECT temp_min AS temp_val FROM em500_pt100_sap WHERE batch_no = s.batch_no
        ) AS AllTemps
    ) AS [Min Temperature],

    (
        SELECT MAX(temp_val) --  2 
        FROM (
            SELECT temp_max AS temp_val FROM em320_th_sap WHERE batch_no = s.batch_no
            UNION ALL
            SELECT temp_max AS temp_val FROM em500_pt100_sap WHERE batch_no = s.batch_no
        ) AS AllTemps
    ) AS [Max Temperature],

    --  TEMPERATURE (:  + )
    (
        SELECT AVG(temp_val)
        FROM (
            SELECT temp_avg AS temp_val FROM em320_th_sap WHERE batch_no = s.batch_no
            UNION ALL
            SELECT temp_avg AS temp_val FROM em500_pt100_sap WHERE batch_no = s.batch_no
        ) AS AllTemps
    ) AS [Average Temperature],


    --  HUMIDITY ()
    (SELECT MIN(humid_min) FROM em320_th_sap WHERE batch_no = s.batch_no) AS [Min Humidity],
    (SELECT MAX(humid_max) FROM em320_th_sap WHERE batch_no = s.batch_no) AS [Max Humidity],
    (SELECT AVG(humid_avg) FROM em320_th_sap WHERE batch_no = s.batch_no) AS [Average Humidity],
    


    --  OZONE
    (SELECT MIN(oz_min) FROM o3_sap WHERE batch_no = s.batch_no) AS [Min Ozone],
    (SELECT MAX(oz_max) FROM o3_sap WHERE batch_no = s.batch_no) AS [Max Ozone],
    (SELECT AVG(oz_avg) FROM o3_sap WHERE batch_no = s.batch_no) AS [Average Ozone]
    

FROM sap s
ORDER BY s.StartDateTime DESC;

/* 1.  (CTE)  AllData  */
WITH AllData AS (
    /* EM500 - Temp */
    SELECT id, batch_no, site_id, 'Temperature' AS parameter, temp_min AS min, temp_max AS max, temp_avg AS avg
    FROM em500_pt100_sap
    UNION ALL
    /* O3 - Ozone */
    SELECT id, batch_no, site_id, 'Ozone', oz_min, oz_max, oz_avg
    FROM o3_sap
    UNION ALL
    /* EM320 - Temp */
    SELECT id, batch_no, site_id, 'Temperature', temp_min, temp_max, temp_avg
    FROM em320_th_sap
    UNION ALL
    /* EM320 - Humid */
    SELECT id, batch_no, site_id, 'Humidity', humid_min, humid_max, humid_avg
    FROM em320_th_sap
)

/* 2.  AllData  Join  site_detail */
SELECT 
    d.batch_no,
    s.site_name,      --  Site 
    d.parameter,      --  Temp, Humid  Ozone
    d.min,
    d.max,
    d.avg
FROM AllData d
LEFT JOIN site_detail s ON d.site_id = s.id --  site_id  id 
ORDER BY d.batch_no desc

SELECT TOP(100)[batch_no] as 'Batch no.'
      ,[wh_location] as 'WHLocation'
      ,[temp_min]
      ,[temp_max]
      ,[temp_avg]
      ,[humid_min]
      ,[humid_max]
      ,[humid_avg]
  FROM [dbo].[sap_fg_table] ORDER BY batch_no desc
